dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, hachures and spot heights. Inset: Berlin und weitere Umgegend. In upper margin: Stielers Hand-Atlas. No. [?]. Berichtigt von C. Scherrer. Probably issued in: Stielers Hand-Atlas ... Gotha : Justus Perthes, 1912. Historic Maps copy originally folded in covers 18 x 11 cm.
